            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight">
            <div class="highlight-icon">‚ö°</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Quick Response</h4>
              <p>I'll get back to you within 24-48 hours</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight">
            <div class="highlight-icon">üåè</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Australia-Wide Service</h4>
